Package hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.element

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ButtonGuiElement
    A GUI element that displays text and can be clicked.
    CheckboxGuiElement
    A GUI element that can be checked and unchecked.
    ContinuousSliderGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a continuous, non-discrete slider, with text on top of it.
    ContinuousSliderGuiElement.ProgressedAction
    The handler of the progress changed action.
    DiscreteSliderGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a discrete, non-continuous slider, with text on top of it.
    DiscreteSliderGuiElement.ProgressedAction
    The handler of the progress changed action.
    DropdownGuiElement
    A GUI element that allows viewers to select a single value from a list of choices.
    DropdownGuiElement.ChosenAction
    The handler of the chosen action.
    ProgressBarGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a progress bar.
    RadioButtonGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a radio button.
    RadioButtonGuiElement.CheckedAction
    The handler of the checked action.
    RadioButtonGuiElement.UncheckedAction
    The handler of the unchecked action.
    RectangleGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a colored rectangle.
    TextFieldGuiElement
    A GUI element that is a text input field.
    TextFieldGuiElement.TextChangedAction
    The handler of the text changed action.
    TextGuiElement
    A GUI element that displays text.
    TextureGuiElement
    A GUI element that displays a texture and can be clicked.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TextGuiElement.Alignment
    Represents directions to which texts can be aligned.
